snippet.title: Super Boxing Championship! - Download Free Physics Boxing Simulation Mobile Game
snippet.description:
Knock out your foes using a full body physics interaction system with simulated weight and collision.

Brawl against an infinite number of random opponents of all skill levels and backgrounds. Earn cash to unlock items such as outfits, hairstyles, and emotes! Battle in an exhibition match or an eight-man bracket tournament. 

Download for free on iOS and Android devices on the App Store or Google Play!
Google Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.stickrunningsupreme.sbc
App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/super-boxing-championship/id1578229268
